name: .21 GIZZY THE CAT & LUCY NATURE WALK (TEXEL ISLAND, NL). Lucky Lucy van Delft
description: Gizzy the amazing 16 yr old cat happily walks herself thru the woods on Texel Island in North Holland, wearing her new homemade sweater. Clearly she's into it. Mainly this is a public service announcement to please take your cat(s) with you on vacation. Thank you in advance for your prompt attention to this matter. This was created for the #objkt4objkt event and also #girlsgang promo featuring the lady NFT artists (and cats). *sound on* to hear the birds and maybe my annoying "talking to the cat" voice. thanks to kapwing for the video editing software FREE ONLINE.
